show.description: This film tells the story of a young woman from a rural village — innocent at heart, free from deceit or malice. Armed only with her talent earned through sheer hard work, she arrives in the city in search of her future groom. What unfolds is a delightful journey filled with humorous and heartwarming experiences. With plenty of moments to make you smile, this charming film is sure to win your heart. Watch "Deadly Temptation" now!
